  "title": "Admin Assistant",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Collaborate with our administrative team to deliver an exceptional customer experience across all areas of the company.</li>\n  <li>Review purchase orders (POs) and delivery orders (DOs) from internal and external parties to ensure accuracy in items, quantities, and amounts.</li>\n  <li>Perform data entry tasks to maintain accurate records.</li>\n  <li>Handle filing, document verification, and checks efficiently.</li>\n  <li>Manage office administration tasks, including answering phone calls.</li>\n  <li>Stay well-organized, detail-oriented, and capable of thriving in a fast-paced environment.</li>\n  <li>Assist with human resources and payroll-related activities.</li>\n  <li>Undertake additional administrative or accounts-related duties as assigned.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be contacted. All applications will be handled confidentially. By submitting your application, you agree to the collection, use, retention, and disclosure of your personal information to prospective employers.</p>\n<p>Wecruit Pte Ltd</p>\n<p>EA License No: 20C0270</p>",
